immediately.</i>

3
00:00:03,567 --> 00:00:06,467
<i>I'm not leaving this house!
You're f**king useless!</i>

4
00:00:08,167 --> 00:00:09,667
<i> My goodness, Althea!</i>

5
00:00:09,667 --> 00:00:10,733
<i> Where have you been?</i>

6
00:00:10,733 --> 00:00:12,567
<i>Your father and I
were worried about you.</i>

7
00:00:12,567 --> 00:00:14,833
<i>I heard there was
a corpse found buried</i>

8
00:00:14,833 --> 00:00:16,800
<i>at Uncle Edward's
old house.</i>

9
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:18,300
<i>So, I visited him
and checked on him.</i>

10
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:19,633
<i>Don't do that ever
again, okay?</i>

11
00:00:19,633 --> 00:00:22,267
<i>What good would your apology
do if you were killed or raped?</i>

12
00:00:22,267 --> 00:00:23,167
<i> Were you a rape victim?</i>

13
00:00:23,167 --> 00:00:25,733
<i>Am I the daughter
of your rapist?</i>

14
00:00:25,733 --> 00:00:27,400
<i> Ma, you lied?</i>

15
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,133
<i>At that time, I thought
that was what I had to do</i>

16
00:00:30,133 --> 00:00:32,400
<i>to send Louisa's
murderer  to jail.</i>

17
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:35,400
<i>Someone was imprisoned
because of your lie!</i>

18
00:00:35,433 --> 00:00:36,933
<i> That's not enough, Ma!</i>

19
00:00:36,933 --> 00:00:38,933
<i>I guess you're all worked
up in there.</i>

20
00:00:38,933 --> 00:00:41,133
<i>I hope you all liked
my gift.</i>

21
00:00:41,133 --> 00:00:42,600
<i> You think you can ruin me?</i>

22
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,767
<i> You can't destroy me, Mel.</i>

23
00:00:44,767 --> 00:00:46,467
